	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habes hic <persName type="auto_name">Paulum Knippe</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l640" cert="high">Flandrum</placeName>, <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Geneva</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugduno</placeName> redeuntem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Is praeterquam quod a <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> et aliis multas tibi literas affert, vivę quoque epistolae loco esse poterit et narrare, quęcunque vel <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l167" cert="high">Genevę</placeName> vel <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l301" cert="high">Lugduni</placeName> vidit et audivit ipse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quibus ut ego quicquam addam, operae precium non est.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsit per eundem <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> ad me quoque, quas tibi communicarem, nisi scirem eadem ipsum ad te quoque scribere.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Res in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> satis sunt exulceratae adhuc; orandus itaque, ut dominus illis et nobis succurrat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="auto_name">Badena</placeName> nihildum habemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Speraveram futurum, ut <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaronensium</placeName> res componeretur; sed finito nunc concilio nescio, quid sperare debeam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Metuo, ne illud magnorum inter nos in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetia</placeName> tumultuum occasio futurum sit; <foreign xml:lang="de">dann uff das ist es bißhar alles gspillt.</foreign></s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Sind si aber witzig (die anderen), so lassend si uns zefriden; dann unser undergang kan on iren großen schaden nitt geschehen.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><foreign xml:lang="la">Vicini nostri <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l160" cert="high">Friburgenses</placeName> et <placeName ref="l760" cert="high">Solodorenses</placeName></foreign> sind vast kützlig; weiß nitt, was in inen stecket; vilicht bißt si die hut.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gott welle uns vor unfal bhuͤten!</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l167" cert="high">genffisch</placeName> sach ist dermaß, das schier nitt darvon zschryben noch zreden.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Profugerant exules ex ditione dominorum nostrorum; nunc nescio, quae illis iterum lux illis affulgeat: catervatim, ut audio, redeunt, <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevensibus</placeName> insultant, se excusant, calumniis et mendaciis omnia complent, cum certo certius constet ipsos perditos esse nebulones.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed odia illa inveterata faciunt, ut inveniant aures, apud quos non deberent invenire.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sabaudus se quoque excusat, ut nesciam, quo adhuc sit res evasura.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectamus nunc conventum proxim mense <placeName type="citizen_name">Neoduni</placeName> futurum; <foreign xml:lang="de">da wirt man aber tagen, bis es wider nacht wirt.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expecto, ut tu scribas multa.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amici omnes recte valent et te salutant, praesertim <persName ref="p8063" cert="high">Steigerus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Nägelinus</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Grafenriett</persName>, socer, <persName type="auto_name">Zehenderi</persName> et multi alii.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutem dic tuis omnibus meo et uxoris nomine.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> 16. ianuarii 1563.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">I[ohannes] Hall[erus</persName>] tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
